-->Numerical simulations of the paper
	"Parallel-in-time integration of the shallow water equations on the rotating sphere using Parareal and MGRIT"
	by J. G. Caldas Steinstraesser, P. da Silva Peixoto and Martin Schreiber
	submitted to the Journal of Computational Physics

--> Test cases:
	:: Three Gaussian bumps
	:: Unstable jet (Galewsky)

--> Run:
	source 0_configure
	./1_run_everything

